# Hortus Garden & Landscape
Professional Landscaping Services in Pensacola, Florida

## Transform Your Outdoor Space in Pensacola, Florida
Get expert landscaping solutions tailored to your needs in Pensacola and surrounding areas. From custom landscape design to professional lawn maintenance, we bring your vision to life with quality craftsmanship and Florida landscaping expertise.

## Professional Landscaping Services in Pensacola, Florida
Comprehensive landscaping solutions for residential and commercial properties throughout Pensacola, Gulf Breeze, Navarre, and surrounding Florida areas

### Landscape Design in Pensacola
Custom landscape design and planning services for Florida properties, specializing in native plants and climate-appropriate solutions

#### What's Included:
- Site analysis and soil testing
- Custom design consultation
- 3D landscape visualization
- Plant selection for Florida climate
- Professional installation
- 1-year plant warranty

#### Starting at $2,500
Price varies by property size and complexity

### Lawn Maintenance & Care
Professional lawn care and maintenance services for Pensacola homes and businesses, including mowing, fertilization, and weed control

#### What's Included:
- Weekly or bi-weekly mowing
- Edge trimming and cleanup
- Fertilization program
- Weed control treatment
- Seasonal lawn care
- Equipment and supplies included

#### Starting at $150/month
Based on property size and frequency

### Tree & Shrub Care Services
Expert tree trimming, pruning, and shrub care services for Florida landscapes, ensuring healthy growth and storm resistance

